{"tid":988442,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【身體力行】撐患癌好友做化療 大姐明捨身剃光頭","createTime":"2019-01-20T05:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T02:46:47.000Z","uid":130626,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4690ce14c0146d4e8dc1270cd21aa44ea150004a","tid":988442,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T05:28:49.000Z","msg":"林建明（大姐明）同萬綺雯今日喺欣澳出席心晴行動慈善基金主辦嘅第十屆「心晴跑．跑傳情」活動，原本戴帽嘅大姐明，主動除帽大晒光頭：「我個朋友患癌要做化療，做完開始脫髮，我叫佢不如剃咗佢啦，又靚又唔使煩，跟住我就陪佢一齊剃。」大姐明笑指40年前拍電影《社女》，已經做咗時代先驅剃過頭：「而家剃都依然咁靚，其實剃咗頭真係好爽，我朋友都有被我感動呀，而家心情都好啲，仲繼續做化療。」身旁嘅萬綺雯大讚大姐明有勇氣。<br />\n大姐明亦話好開心見到萬綺雯，讚佢依然又弗又靚：「你生活、家庭好嗎？如果生活有咩問題，要即刻解決，揾啲方法幫自己，唔好屈喺心呀。」萬綺雯即笑住解釋：「我冇事，好好，大家唔使擔心，只係放個長假。呢年都係睇中醫、調理身體，屋企有人唔舒服，自己都想抽時間陪佢哋，冇事嘅，如果開工都等新年後先啦。」大姐明都話人生唔止得工作，都要抽時間陪屋企人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190120/large/1547955940_5808.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190120%2Flarge%2F1547955940_5808.jpg&h=00396689&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190120/large/1547955941_5abe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190120%2Flarge%2F1547955941_5abe.jpg&h=0a299d69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190120/large/1547955947_65b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190120%2Flarge%2F1547955947_65b8.jpg&h=4df2e490&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190120/59163356\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190120%2F59163356&d=dvib9FR1LnYQWVcXPKKa4o9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=38b1f209\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190120%2F59163356&h=bf0e5606\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190120/59163356</a>"},{"pid":"9b71b121d13ae04b89ded2506ce06b90c97b28b0","tid":988442,"uid":55523,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T05:45:40.000Z","msg":"最尾張相有少少似tb攬女"},{"pid":"adf85eb70615af950908c99b95c1ac37517bb33a","tid":988442,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T06:09:06.000Z","msg":"大姐明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af164c459dee5016c70659f5de6950de29954280","tid":988442,"uid":221490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T06:13:06.000Z","msg":"萬二蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df0772f6c1c78e1c1057caaa2ec55ee2f8a3b2f","tid":988442,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T06:15:41.000Z","msg":"大姐明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb735169edee19cd028d1a0feb7f16c255cb6d4","tid":988442,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T06:18:33.000Z","msg":"星空下的傾情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0195794e4e768cc29ef19c34a9064f74834f3176","tid":988442,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T06:51:33.000Z","msg":"「我可以無髮，你不能無法！」中國709案律師妻子集體剃髮，抗議當局非法辦案<br />\n<img src=\"https://amp.dw.com/image/46781728_304.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Famp.dw.com%2Fimage%2F46781728_304.jpeg&h=0a530aba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本周一，4名在押中國維權律師的妻子集體剃光所有頭髮，抗議中國司法當局「非法辦案」。她們在公開剃髮之後，還一同前往最高人民法院，並且通過接待室提交了《督促函》。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.storm.mg/article/726644\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Farticle%2F726644&d=dvib9FR1LnYQWVcXPKKa4o9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=180ac882\" target=\"_blank\"